snippet.title: Impulse Rogue - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a glimpse into the depths of the psyche in Impulse Rogue, a haunting souls-like action-RPG where you will face Yelena's inner demons and make choices that will shape your destiny.

Wishlist Impulse Rogue on Steam Today! https://steam.pm/app/1910800
